1) Step 1: Create New Connection
Open MQTTBox and click Create MQTT Client.

Configure:
Client Name : Generator Monitor
Protocol    : MQTT/TCP
Broker Host : broker.hivemq.com
Port        : 1883

Click Connect.

2) Step 2: Subscribe to Topic

Subscribe to:
generator/status

3) Step 3: Monitor Incoming Data

After successful connection, MQTTBox starts receiving generator telemetry data from ESP8266.

------------------------
Sample MQTT Payload
{
  "fuelLevel": 74,
  "coolantTemp": 86,
  "batteryVoltage": 12.7,
  "engineRPM": 1500,
  "runHours": 324,
  "totalPower": 42.5,
  "engineStatus": "RUNNING"
}
